components.text: [b][color=#000000][size=21]Free Text Orders: How many free-text orders are processed?[/size][/color][/b]

[size=15][b][color=#000000] Free-text orders are defined as orders without purchase requisitions, material  number and contract usage and therefore do not take advantage of economies of
scale or contract usage.[/color][/b][/size]
[color=#000000][size=15][b]  Financial impact =  value of free text purchase orders (<%=Currency%>) * reduction potential (%) * better conditions (%) * time factor (x)[/b][/size][/color]
[size=15]savings potentials when using purchase req, contracts and material numbers (%) (discounts etc.)[/size]

formulas.name: EDI RATIO
formulas.text:
SUM(
CASE 
    WHEN COALESCE("EKPO"."KONNR", '' )= '' AND 
    PROCESS NOT EQUALS 'Lege BANF Position an' AND 
    COALESCE("EKPO"."MATNR", '' )= ''
    THEN "EKPO"."NETWR_CONVERTED" 
    ELSE 0.0 
END)

components.text: [size=15][b] Total number of free text orders[/b][/size]

formulas.name: Sales Orders
formulas.text:
SUM(
CASE 
    WHEN COALESCE("EKPO"."KONNR", '' )= '' AND 
    PROCESS NOT EQUALS 'Lege BANF Position an' AND 
    COALESCE("EKPO"."MATNR", '' )= ''
    THEN 1.0 
    ELSE 0.0 
END)
